on Discord (thank you and keep it coming):\n> Implemented new hand tracking solution from Meta\n> Added support button to dialogs for when things go wrong.\n> 1 fish per player in fishing tutorial\n> Added check to ensure both players are on the same version\n> Added Discord button so you can join the community (note, you may need to search about a bit for where the window was spawned)", "created_date": 1733719867, "id": "8823040447731132", "version": "0.2.48", "version_code": 48, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "8603854472983065", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8823040447731132"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "532812109502638"}]}, "change_log": "Let\u2019s get the party rockin\u2019 with some major updates!\n\n> 44% smoother Physics!\n> The game can now be launched multiplayer from the same primary account across multiple devices (app sharing must be turned off). This means less copies need to be purchased!\n> Balloon Bunnies now wibbly and wobblier\n> Fixed hang on load when rejoining a game\n> Improved messaging when outside room or controllers are breaking hand tracking\n> Numerous other small bug fixes and improvements\n\nSpotted something we missed, let us know over on discord:\nhttps://discord.com/invite/mDWR7yjXy4", "created_date": 1732762670, "id": "8764053580296486", "version": "0.2.47", "version_code": 47, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typ